{"tid":1354301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］千奇唔好搞班圍村佬上網","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:18:34.000Z","uid":14980,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25690f8c59fa26f25d2f374e4b0ca80f88a291c2","tid":1354301,"uid":14980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E75ujqp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE75ujqp.png&h=1981a337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地靠呢件野上網，唔好剪人地條線！白色線係入屋架！<br />\n仲有水管水制，化糞池，唔好放白蟻紅蟻。你知啦嚴重影響人生活！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNochcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNochcQ.png&h=ca94c964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋人地周圍泊車。周街泊雖然阻到人，但唔好放肽氣、吉爆肽（小心吉爆肽有巨響,無耳塞隨時耳膜穿真係唔好帶埋耳塞入去搞事）可能會有車cam影到呀，唔好諗住帶口罩就做壞事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 以上事情發夢見過，咁搞法佢地好頭痕"},{"pid":"08399c3acafbcc034beb0e1c194155e8f027797d","tid":1354301,"uid":23707,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFqibUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFqibUD.jpg&h=ebc0d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRtS0NX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRtS0NX.jpg&h=7578d7a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n十八鄉連儂牆準備上線啦!"},{"pid":"73657bb8e072c529e9caadfa84a7aaa57426355c","tid":1354301,"uid":14980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"}]}